## Distilled 2026-03-24

### Batch Script Debugging

- **Log with timestamp + exit code** in all batch scripts: `echo [%DATE% %TIME%] Exit: %ERRORLEVEL% >> script.log` <!-- decay:2026-03-24 tier:cold rel:0.385 -->
- Critical for async debugging when human is offline and cannot observe terminal output in real time. <!-- decay:2026-03-24 tier:cold rel:0.385 -->
- Apply to any `.bat`/`.cmd` script running as a scheduled task or background process. <!-- decay:2026-03-24 tier:cold rel:0.385 -->


